# Authentication Middleware - Environment Template

Copy this to `.env.local` and update with your values:

```env
# ============================================================================
# API Configuration
# ============================================================================
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_TIMEOUT=15000

# ============================================================================
# Authentication - Token Configuration
# ============================================================================
# These must match your backend API response field names and cookie names
AUTH_TOKEN_COOKIE_NAME=accessToken
AUTH_REFRESH_COOKIE_NAME=refreshToken
AUTH_TOKEN_EXPIRY_DAYS=7

# ============================================================================
# Authentication - Routes
# ============================================================================
# Configure redirect destinations for authenticated/unauthenticated users
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_LOGIN_ROUTE=/login
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_SIGNUP_ROUTE=/signup
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_VERIFY_ROUTE=/verify
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_FORGOT_PASSWORD_ROUTE=/forgot-password
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_RESET_PASSWORD_ROUTE=/reset-password
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_HOME_ROUTE=/home
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_DASHBOARD_ROUTE=/for-you

# ============================================================================
# Middleware & Debug
# ============================================================================
# Enable detailed middleware logging
DEBUG_AUTH=false
DEBUG_API=false

# ============================================================================
# Environment
# ============================================================================
NODE_ENV=development

# ============================================================================
# Analytics & Tracking (Optional)
# ============================================================================
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=your-ga-id
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=your-sentry-dsn

# ============================================================================
# Feature Flags (Optional)
# ============================================================================
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FEATURE_DARK_MODE=true
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FEATURE_BETA=false
```

---

## 🔑 Token Cookie Configuration

### From Backend
Ensure your backend API returns tokens in this format:

```json
{
  "access_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "refresh_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "token_type": "Bearer",
  "expires_in": 3600,
  "is_verified": true,
  "needs_onboarding": false
}
```

### Cookie Security Settings
The middleware uses these secure settings automatically:
```javascript
cookieOptions: {
  expires: 7,           // 7 days
  path: '/',           // All paths
  secure: true,        // HTTPS only
  sameSite: 'Strict',  // Prevent CSRF
  // Note: httpOnly is set by backend in Set-Cookie header
}
```

---

## 📋 Production Checklist

Before deploying to production:

- [ ] Set `NODE_ENV=production`
- [ ] Set `DEBUG_AUTH=false` (disable logging)
- [ ] Set `DEBUG_API=false`
- [ ] Update `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` to production API endpoint
- [ ] Ensure HTTPS is enabled (required for secure cookies)
- [ ] Verify token refresh endpoint is working: `/v1/auth/refresh`
- [ ] Test token expiry and refresh flow
- [ ] Monitor error logs for auth failures
- [ ] Verify redirect URLs are correct for your domain

---

## 🔐 Security Notes

1. **Never commit** `.env.local` with real credentials
2. **Use `.env.local`** for local development only
3. **Deploy secrets** via environment variable management system
4. **Rotate tokens** regularly (7-30 days recommended)
5. **Monitor token usage** for suspicious patterns

---

## 🧪 Development vs Production

### Development
```env
NODE_ENV=development
DEBUG_AUTH=true
DEBUG_API=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
```

### Staging
```env
NODE_ENV=production
DEBUG_AUTH=false
DEBUG_API=false
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://staging-api.your-domain.com/api
```

### Production
```env
NODE_ENV=production
DEBUG_AUTH=false
DEBUG_API=false
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://api.your-domain.com/api
```
